# Tests

This directory is reserved for PlatformIO tests.

The highest-value tests for this firmware are host-side tests around pure logic:

- LX200 command parsing;
- LX200 response formatting;
- RA/DEC conversion and normalization;
- Modbus coordinate packing and unpacking;
- controller clock behavior;
- route/action logic that can be separated from rendering;
- binary Stellarium packet decoding.

Hardware tests should be kept separate because they require a real ESP32, TFT,
touch controller, RS485 link, and STM32 firmware.
